61
00:09:32,967 --> 00:09:34,383
What's wrong?

62
00:09:35,008 --> 00:09:38,842
The filament got damaged.

63
00:09:39,175 --> 00:09:40,175
Filament?

64
00:09:40,258 --> 00:09:43,842
The thing that lights up.

65
00:09:44,133 --> 00:09:45,883
Isn't that electricity?

66
00:09:46,133 --> 00:09:50,342
The electricity lights the filament,
the filament lights up the bulb.

67
00:09:50,425 --> 00:09:52,758
Oh, yes. I knew that.

68
00:09:53,383 --> 00:09:56,467
So whatever it is,
Install it everywhere.

69
00:09:56,967 --> 00:09:59,800
And give the bills to Majumdar.

70
