government who will support you.

75
00:10:17,467 --> 00:10:20,550
Why do our fathers keep arguing?

76
00:10:20,758 --> 00:10:24,675
My father feels that Zamindar
uncle doesn't understand him

77
00:10:24,883 --> 00:10:29,008
