that my father keeps yakking.

78
00:10:29,467 --> 00:10:31,258
Yakking?

79
00:10:48,758 --> 00:10:49,425
Yes?

80
00:10:49,675 --> 00:10:51,217
My name is Varun Srivastava

81
00:10:51,467 --> 00:10:52,675
