90
00:11:32,383 --> 00:11:33,383
Ask him yourself.

91
00:11:42,842 --> 00:11:43,883
Varun Shrivastava.

92
00:11:43,967 --> 00:11:44,592
Yes?

93
00:11:44,675 --> 00:11:45,925
Don't look back

94
00:11:46,925 --> 00:11:48,717
The driver who drove into you,

95
