because you are not.

99
00:12:03,425 --> 00:12:04,425
Ok.

100
00:12:05,592 --> 00:12:07,550
Which one are you?

101
00:12:08,883 --> 00:12:09,883
Mr. Srivastava

102
00:12:10,717 --> 00:12:12,717
You are very punctual

103
00:12:13,633 --> 00:12:15,550
This is my daughter, Pakhi

104
00:12:15,717 --> 00:12:19,842
And Pakhi,
he is that gentleman I told you about.

105
00:12:20,425 --> 00:12:21,425
Namaste

106
00:12:24,133 --> 00:12:26,008
She wants to be a writer

107
