name starts with 'Archaic'

115
00:13:00,758 --> 00:13:02,008
Where are you staying?

116
00:13:02,092 --> 00:13:05,217
At the Circuit House.
Nearby the temple.

117
00:13:06,133 --> 00:13:08,675
