118
00:13:08,758 --> 00:13:11,508
My motorcycle had
an accident with a car.

119
00:13:12,175 --> 00:13:12,842
In Manekpur?

120
00:13:12,925 --> 00:13:13,925
Yes.

121
00:13:14,217 --> 00:13:15,383
Who was driving?

122
00:13:15,633 --> 00:13:16,717
I was driving.

123
