If you drive both of
them at the same time..

124
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,592
I was driving the motorcycle.

125
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:24,800
Coffee?

126
00:13:25,258 --> 00:13:26,258
Yes

127
00:13:27,175 --> 00:13:29,467
