on such a wide road

129
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:38,300
I don't think these
amateurs should be allowed..

130
00:13:38,967 --> 00:13:41,050
Sorry. I'll get some cold water.

131
00:13:43,175 --> 00:13:44,342
Sorry about that

132
00:14:34,633 --> 00:14:35,967
Baba Nagarjuna.

133
00:14:36,383 --> 00:14:38,217
Real name Vaidyanath Mishra

134
00:14:38,800 --> 00:14:41,133
Lives in Darbhanga, my native village.

135
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:45,092
Where did you say, you are staying?

136
00:15:17,758 --> 00:15:19,967
I'm impressed, Varun Babu.

137
00:15:21,508 --> 00:15:24,675
This mansion instead
of that guest house.

138
00:15:43,467 --> 00:15:45,592
Are you understanding anything,
Debdas Mukherjee?

139
00:15:46,258 --> 00:15:47,592
I can understand everything.

140
00:15:47,842 --> 00:15:49,883
My parents talk exactly like this.

141
00:16:02,967 --> 00:16:04,467
Learn Bengali

142
00:16:06,175 --> 00:16:08,300
You'll have to learn one day

143
