And an even better fighter.

153
00:17:03,133 --> 00:17:05,008
You want to see how he fights?

154
00:17:05,133 --> 00:17:06,633
Like this, while swaying..

155
00:17:07,175 --> 00:17:09,842
No matter how many goons attack him

156
00:17:09,925 --> 00:17:12,633
they will not spoil his hairstyle.

157
00:17:17,758 --> 00:17:18,633
These ruins have remained

158
00:17:18,758 --> 00:17:20,758
