last five hundred years.

159
00:17:20,967 --> 00:17:25,092
Nobody is allowed to build
or demolish anything here.

160
00:17:25,633 --> 00:17:27,675
This famous Radha-Krishna idol is..

161
00:17:27,758 --> 00:17:30,175
..the legacy of my
Roy Chouhdry ancestry.

162
00:17:30,467 --> 00:17:32,592
Its at least three hundred years old.

163
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:37,717
This..

164
