166
00:17:43,967 --> 00:17:46,425
We would need some labourers.

167
00:17:46,592 --> 00:17:47,342
Definitely

168
00:17:47,425 --> 00:17:50,633
So this is where we dig

169
00:17:50,717 --> 00:17:51,217
