170
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:52,300
Digging

171
00:17:52,342 --> 00:17:53,342
Good

172
00:17:53,633 --> 00:17:57,175
Now, do you guys know how to dig?

173
00:17:59,092 --> 00:18:03,717
