the first fish is caught.

190
00:20:07,258 --> 00:20:08,300
Tradition, you see.

191
00:20:08,425 --> 00:20:10,092
Of course.

192
00:20:29,842 --> 00:20:31,842
You are looking in the
wrong direction, Varun babu.

193
00:20:33,258 --> 00:20:34,342
Are you mad?

194
00:20:34,967 --> 00:20:36,633
I was just looking.

195
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:38,925
I saw how you were 'looking'

196
00:20:39,008 --> 00:20:40,008
How was i looking?

197
00:20:40,092 --> 00:20:43,008
Its that 'look'

198
00:20:43,092 --> 00:20:45,800
Things happen.

199
00:20:45,883 --> 00:20:46,967
Nothing happens

200
00:20:47,050 --> 00:20:49,342
your hunger has gone to the brain.

201
00:20:49,425 --> 00:20:51,258
Why are u getting upset?

202
00:20:51,467 --> 00:20:55,175
I am just adding to the
stuff you are already cooking up..

203
00:20:55,550 --> 00:20:57,092
I am not cooking up anything.

204
00:21:47,508 --> 00:21:50,925
