for this painting stuff?

205
00:21:52,217 --> 00:21:54,175
Neither are you Raja, nor Ravi Varma.

206
00:21:55,675 --> 00:21:58,258
You carry that blank
canvas everywhere.

207
00:21:58,342 --> 00:22:00,258
But you never put any paint on it.

208
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:03,342
My dear friend, Debdas

209
00:22:04,842 --> 00:22:07,300
One day I will paint my masterpiece.

210
00:22:08,175 --> 00:22:11,300
And the world will watch.

211
00:22:16,008 --> 00:22:17,800
I want to learn painting.

212
00:22:19,508 --> 00:22:21,925
Why the sudden interest?

213
00:22:22,758 --> 00:22:23,925
Its not sudden.

214
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:25,383
I've always been interested.

215
00:22:26,008 --> 00:22:28,133
You keep talking about.

216
00:22:28,842 --> 00:22:31,008
I've always told you,
I wanted to learn

217
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:32,925
You never told me.

218
00:22:33,008 --> 00:22:36,133
I did you never listen to me.

219
00:22:37,508 --> 00:22:40,800
Fine. Ask Majumdar Babu,
he'll get someone

220
00:22:41,967 --> 00:22:43,342
