230
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:26,300
I mean, when you used
to study in Shantiniketan.

231
00:24:27,342 --> 00:24:30,217
You know that I used
to study in Shantiniketan?

232
00:24:31,675 --> 00:24:35,467
No. As in since you
are the Zamindar's daughter.

233
00:24:38,758 --> 00:24:40,675
I learnt a little.

234
00:24:41,592 --> 00:24:43,800
