235
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:46,508
You tell me.

236
00:24:51,633 --> 00:24:53,633
Lets begin with landscapes.

237
00:24:55,717 --> 00:24:58,175
They are easy to grasp.

238
00:24:58,508 --> 00:25:00,300
