241
00:25:06,133 --> 00:25:08,800
Can't we learn portraits?

242
00:25:12,842 --> 00:25:15,425
You don't think I know
how to paint a landscape?

243
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:17,217
Shall I show you?

244
00:25:40,758 --> 00:25:44,883
You know how to paint.

245
00:25:48,258 --> 00:25:52,758
