246
00:25:55,092 --> 00:25:56,092
Leaves!

247
00:25:57,925 --> 00:25:59,592
They are really easy

248
00:26:00,633 --> 00:26:01,925
Show me.

249
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,133
Sure

250
00:26:27,717 --> 00:26:29,383
Take some green

