253
00:26:55,633 --> 00:26:56,633
Leaves

254
00:26:58,842 --> 00:26:59,842
This?

255
00:27:04,717 --> 00:27:06,717
Its Modern Art.

256
00:27:13,217 --> 00:27:15,967
You don't know how to paint, do you?

257
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:26,008
So you are a teacher to him?

258
00:27:26,175 --> 00:27:30,425
For the class to run,
someone has to be a teacher

259
00:27:31,758 --> 00:27:35,967
Someone is too smart for his own good.

260
00:27:36,758 --> 00:27:39,092
I always wanted to learn painting.

261
00:27:39,425 --> 00:27:40,651
And this is a good opportunity. No?

262
00:27:40,675 --> 00:27:41,675
Of course.

263
00:30:30,758 --> 00:30:33,592
My father calls me Pakhi Express

264
00:30:33,842 --> 00:30:36,300
Because I'm always in a hurry

265
00:30:37,425 --> 00:30:39,217
What do you want to do?

266
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,758
I want to write.

267
00:30:41,592 --> 00:30:43,675
Lots and lots of books.

268
00:30:45,508 --> 00:30:47,883
Sometimes, I feel like running away

269
00:30:47,967 --> 00:30:50,383
